<p class="indent2" style="-uslm-lc:I13" xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/" xmlns:dcterms="http://purl.org/dc/terms/" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance">The base period taken into account for purposes of paragraph (1)(B) with respect to individuals separating from service with the employer after <date date="1994-12-31">December 31, 1994</date>, is the calendar quarter beginning July 1 of the calendar year preceding the calendar year in which such separation occurs.</p>
